            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2009-05-13" class="main-meta">2009-05-13 21:57:15</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1822862/">云南人民出版社2006版</a>
